{"word":"mauvais","priority":"★★★","meanings":[{"part_of_speech":"adjective","definition":"悪い、良くない","english_definition":"bad, not good","examples":[{"sentence":"C'est un mauvais film.","translation":"それは悪い映画だ。"},{"sentence":"J'ai passé une mauvaise journée.","translation":"私は悪い一日を過ごした。"},{"sentence":"Il a un mauvais caractère.","translation":"彼は悪い性格だ。"}],"collocations":["mauvais temps (悪天候)","mauvaise nouvelle (悪い知らせ)","mauvaise humeur (不機嫌)","mauvais élève (出来の悪い生徒)","mauvaise qualité (悪い品質)"],"synonyms":["méchant","incorrect","défavorable","nuisible"],"antonyms":["bon","bien","excellent","favorable"]},{"part_of_speech":"adjective","definition":"下手な、不得意な","english_definition":"bad at, not skilled at","examples":[{"sentence":"Je suis mauvais en maths.","translation":"私は数学が苦手だ。"},{"sentence":"Il est mauvais joueur.","translation":"彼は負けず嫌いだ（良いプレイヤーではない）。"}],"collocations":["mauvais en (～が下手)","mauvais joueur (負けず嫌い)"],"synonyms":["inepte","inhabile"],"antonyms":["bon","doué"]},{"part_of_speech":"adjective","definition":"ひどい、深刻な","english_definition":"serious, severe","examples":[{"sentence":"Il a une mauvaise blessure.","translation":"彼はひどい怪我をしている。"},{"sentence":"La situation est mauvaise.","translation":"状況は深刻だ。"}],"collocations":["mauvais état (悪い状態)","mauvaise passe (苦境)"],"synonyms":["grave","sérieux"],"antonyms":["léger","bénin"]},{"part_of_speech":"adverb","definition":"悪く、まずく","english_definition":"badly","examples":[{"sentence":"Il chante mauvais.","translation":"彼は歌が下手だ。"},{"sentence":"Ça sent mauvais.","translation":"それは臭い。"}],"collocations":["sentir mauvais (臭い)"],"synonyms":["mal"],"antonyms":["bien"]}],"etymology":{"value":"ラテン語の「malus」（悪い）に由来します。","priority":"★★☆"},"pronunciation":{"ipa":"/movɛ/","syllables":"mau-vais"},"inflection":{"gender":"masculine","plural":"mauvais","feminine":"mauvaise","feminine_plural":"mauvaises"},"usage_notes":{"explanation":"「mauvais」は非常に一般的な形容詞で、様々な状況で「悪い」という意味を表します。人の性格、物の品質、状況の深刻さなど、幅広い対象に使用できます。また、副詞的に使われることもあります。女性形は「mauvaise」となります。","priority":"★★★"},"common_mistakes":{"examples":[{"incorrect":"*C'est un bon mauvais film.*","correct":"C'est un mauvais film.","note":"「bon mauvais」のような表現は通常使いません。"},{"incorrect":"*Je suis mauvais à le français.*","correct":"Je suis mauvais en français.","note":"「～が下手」と言う場合は、「mauvais en + 名詞」の形を使います。"}],"priority":"★★☆"},"related_words":{"derivatives":["mauvaisement (副詞: 悪く)","mauvaiseté (名詞: 悪意)"],"expressions":["être de mauvaise humeur (不機嫌である)","passer un mauvais quart d'heure (嫌な思いをする)","avoir mauvaise mine (顔色が悪い)","prendre quelque chose en mauvaise part (～を悪く取る)"],"priority":"★★★"},"level_frequency":{"CEFR":"A1","frequency_google_ngram":"非常に高頻度","priority":"★☆☆"},"readability_explanation":{"level":"A1","text":"「Mauvais」は「悪い」という意味のフランス語の単語です。例えば、「C'est mauvais」（それは悪い）のように使います。食べ物が美味しくないときや、天気があまり良くないときなど、色々な場面で使えます。覚えておくととても便利な単語です。"},"example_sentences":[{"sentence":"Ce restaurant a une mauvaise réputation.","translation":"このレストランは評判が悪い。","type":"adjective","meaning_category":"悪い"},{"sentence":"Il a fait un mauvais choix.","translation":"彼は悪い選択をした。","type":"adjective","meaning_category":"悪い"},{"sentence":"Je me sens mauvais aujourd'hui.","translation":"今日は気分が悪い。","type":"adjective","meaning_category":"悪い"},{"sentence":"Elle chante mauvais.","translation":"彼女は歌が下手だ。","type":"adverb","meaning_category":"悪く"}]}